"text='Heals'</ref> ability will heal each allied adjacent unit, usually "
"<ref>dst='ability_heals +4' text='4HP'</ref> or <ref>dst='ability_heals +8' "
"text='8HP'</ref> per turn, or prevent Poison from causing that unit damage."
